data.description: This home is STUNNING!!! It is an ABSOLUTE DREAM from the moment you enter the extended entryway boasting 12ft ceilings, the large formal dining room and study with beautiful French Doors. Recent upgrades including new paint,carpet,epoxy garage, and lighting enhance its beauty. With architectural archways and ample space for entertaining, this home is perfect for hosting gatherings.  Enjoy the ultimate outdoor experience which features a large corner lot with a wraparound extended covered back patio, the front features a Reserve facing the home (no front neighbors), stained interior fence, BEAUTIFUL!! updated landscaping, full gutters around the home, and sprinklers system. This is a must-see!!! Don't' miss out on this premier property in a prime location!
